<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Your Order Has Shipped - <%= siteName %></title>
  <style>
    /* Reset styles */
    body, html {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
    }
    
    /* Container */
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
    
    /* Header */
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    
    .logo {
      max-width: 150px;
      height: auto;
    }
    
    /* Content */
    .content {
      padding: 0 20px 20px;
    }
    
    h1 {
      color: #2c3e50;
      font-size: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    
    p {
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    
    /* Order details */
    .order-details {
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    
    .order-details p {
      margin: 5px 0;
    }
    
    .order-number {
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #2c3e50;
    }
    
    .shipping-info {
      background-color: #e8f4fc;
      border-left: 4px solid #3498db;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    
    .shipping-info h3 {
      margin-top: 0;
      color: #2c3e50;
    }
    
    .tracking-number {
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #e67e22;
    }
    
    /* Button */
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #3498db;
      color: white !important;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 12px 25px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    
    /* Footer */
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
      color: #7f8c8d;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    
    .social-links {
      margin: 15px 0;
    }
    
    .social-links a {
      margin: 0 10px;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #3498db;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <a href="<%= siteUrl %>">
        <img src="<%= siteLogo %>" alt="<%= siteName %>" class="logo">
      </a>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <h1>Your Order Has Shipped!</h1>
      
      <p>Hello <%= user.name %>,</p>
      
      <p>Great news! Your order <span class="order-number">#<%= order.orderNumber || order._id %></span> has been shipped and is on its way to you.</p>
      
      <div class="shipping-info">
        <h3>Shipping Information</h3>
        
        <% if (trackingInfo && trackingInfo.number) { %>
          <p><strong>Tracking Number:</strong> <span class="tracking-number"><%= trackingInfo.number %></span></p>
          <p><strong>Shipping Carrier:</strong> <%= trackingInfo.carrier || 'Standard Shipping' %></p>
          <p><strong>Estimated Delivery:</strong> <%= trackingInfo.estimatedDelivery ? new Date(trackingInfo.estimatedDelivery).toLocaleDateString() : '3-5 business days' %></p>
          
          <% if (trackingInfo.url) { %>
            <p style="margin-top: 15px;">
              <a href="<%= trackingInfo.url %>" class="button" target="_blank">Track Your Package</a>
            </p>
          <% } %>
        <% } else { %>
          <p>Your order is on its way! We'll send you tracking information as soon as it's available.</p>
        <% } %>
      </div>
      
      <div class="order-details">
        <p><strong>Order Number:</strong> #<%= order.orderNumber || order._id %></p>
        <p><strong>Shipped On:</strong> <%= new Date(order.shippedAt || new Date()).toLocaleDateString() %></p>
        <p><strong>Shipping To:</strong> 
          <%= order.shippingAddress.address %>, 
          <% if (order.shippingAddress.address2) { %>
            <%= order.shippingAddress.address2 %>, 
          <% } %>
          <%= order.shippingAddress.city %>, 
          <%= order.shippingAddress.state %> 
          <%= order.shippingAddress.postalCode %>, 
          <%= order.shippingAddress.country %>
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <p>You can view the status of your order by clicking the button below:</p>
      
      <p style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="<%= siteUrl %>/orders/<%= order._id %>" class="button">View Order Details</a>
      </p>
      
      <p>If you have any questions about your order, please don't hesitate to contact our customer service team at <a href="mailto:<%= supportEmail %>"><%= supportEmail %></a>.</p>
      
      <p>Thank you for shopping with us!</p>
      
      <p>Best regards,<br>The <%= siteName %> Team</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> <%= siteName %>. All rights reserved.</p>
      
      <div class="social-links">
        <a href="<%= socialLinks.facebook %>" target="_blank">Facebook</a>
        <a href="<%= socialLinks.twitter %>" target="_blank">Twitter</a>
        <a href="<%= socialLinks.instagram %>" target="_blank">Instagram</a>
      </div>
      
      <p>
        <a href="<%= siteUrl %>/privacy">Privacy Policy</a> | 
        <a href="<%= siteUrl %>/terms">Terms of Service</a> | 
        <a href="<%= siteUrl %>/contact">Contact Us</a>
      </p>
      
      <p>
        <small>
          This email was sent to <%= user.email %>. 
          <a href="<%= unsubscribeUrl %>" style="color: #7f8c8d;">Unsubscribe</a>.
        </small>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
